categories: Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Oorrl Morm was a male Ithorian Jedi Master of the Jedi Order. Master Morm served on the Jedi planet Ossus, and participated in a battle on the planet Ithor against a vicious band of pirates. Morm sacrificed his life to delay the attacks of the pirates. Following Morm's sacrifice, a Galactic Republic Navy warship arrived and took the criminals into custody.
